# VHS Script: VSCode Integration Demo
# Shows how ccu runs in VSCode's integrated terminal

Output ../images/09-settings-mode.gif

# Terminal settings
Set FontSize 17
Set Width 1200
Set Height 830
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 0.05s
Set Padding 10 

Hide

# Start the program
Type "ccu --anon"
Enter
Sleep 10s

# Switch views
Type "s"
Sleep 10s

Show 
Sleep 3s

